Package frc.robot.io.interfaces

Interface MotorIO

All Known Implementing Classes:
MotorIOArmStub, MotorIOBase, MotorIOElevatorStub, MotorIOFlywheelStub, MotorIOSparkMax, MotorIOStub
public interface MotorIO
This is a generic definition for the Motor IO interface. All motor controllers (SparkMax, Talon, Kraken, etc) are expected to provide this basic functionality

      Optional: Run closed loop (using a PID) at a specific velocity
      Parameters:
      velocityRadPerSec - desired velocity
      ffVolts - feedforward voltage which depends on the static friction of what is connected to the motor
